# 通过Analytics Zoo在Apache Spark上使用Keras/Tensorflow
Keras/Tensorflow是受到广泛使用的机器学习库。在这个Notebook中，我们会看到如何通过Analytics Zoo，在Apache Spark上使用Keras/Tensorflow训练机器学习模型。

## 准备数据
我们使用MNIST数据。MNIST数据是一个面向初学者的手写数字识别数据集。从[MNIST官方网站](http://yann.lecun.com/exdb/mnist/)上下载数据。

### 上传数据到COS
[COS](https://cloud.tencent.com/product/cos)是腾讯云上的对象存储系统。我们将刚才下载的四个文件上传到[COS存储桶](https://console.cloud.tencent.com/cos5/bucket/setting?type=filelist&bucketName=ds-1257305158&path=%252F&region=ap-shanghai)中，进行下一步的处理。

%md
2.从COS下载MNIST的数据

%pyspark
from bigdl.dataset.mnist import extract_images,extract_labels

def get_mnist_from_cos():
    def download_file(from_path, to_path=None):
        response = client.get_object(
            Bucket='demo-1258997244',
            Key=from_path
        )
        to_path = '/tmp/{}'.format(from_path.split("/")[-1])
        response['Body'].get_stream_to_file(to_path)
        return to_path
    with open(download_file("/mnist/train-images-idx3-ubyte.gz"), 'rb') as f:
        train_images = extract_images(f)
        
    with open( download_file('/mnist/train-labels-idx1-ubyte.gz'), 'rb') as f:
        train_labels = extract_labels(f)
        
    with open( download_file('/mnist/t10k-images-idx3-ubyte.gz'), 'rb') as f:
        test_images = extract_images(f)
    
    with open( download_file('/mnist/t10k-labels-idx1-ubyte.gz'), 'rb') as f:
        test_labels = extract_labels(f)
    
    return train_images, train_labels, test_images, test_labels
    
train_images, train_labels, test_images, test_labels = get_mnist_from_cos()

%md
4.将数据加载进Spark，并进行归一化

msg.data: 4.将数据加载进Spark，并进行归一化

paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
from bigdl.dataset import mnist

train_image_rdd = sc.parallelize(train_images)
train_label_rdd = sc.parallelize(train_labels)
test_image_rdd = sc.parallelize(test_images)
test_label_rdd = sc.parallelize(test_labels)

training_rdd = train_image_rdd.zip(train_label_rdd).map(lambda rec_tuple: ((rec_tuple[0] - mnist.TRAIN_MEAN) / mnist.TRAIN_STD, np.array(rec_tuple[1])))
testing_rdd = test_image_rdd.zip(test_label_rdd).map(lambda rec_tuple: ((rec_tuple[0] - mnist.TRAIN_MEAN) / mnist.TRAIN_STD, np.array(rec_tuple[1])))

## 模型训练
1.通过Tensorflow的Keras API定义一个CNN模型

模型训练

1.通过Tensorflow的Keras API定义一个CNN模型

paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
import tensorflow as tf

model = tf.keras.Sequential([
    tf.keras.layers.Flatten(input_shape=(28, 28, 1)),
    tf.keras.layers.Dense(64, activation='relu'),
    tf.keras.layers.Dense(64, activation='relu'),
    tf.keras.layers.Dense(10, activation='softmax'),
])

model.compile(optimizer='rmsprop', loss='sparse_categorical_crossentropy', metrics=['accuracy'])

%md
2.通过Intel Analytics Zoo库将单机模型分布式，从而可以在Spark上进行分布式训练

msg.data: 2.通过Intel Analytics Zoo库将单机模型分布式，从而可以在Spark上进行分布式训练

paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
from zoo.tfpark import KerasModel

keras_model = KerasModel(model)

%md
3.开始训练模型

%pyspark
from zoo.tfpark import TFDataset
from zoo import init_nncontext
import numpy as np

init_nncontext()
max_epoch = 5

dataset = TFDataset.from_rdd(
    training_rdd,
    features=(tf.float32, [28, 28, 1]),
    labels=(tf.int32, []),
    batch_size=320,
    val_rdd=testing_rdd
)


keras_model.fit(dataset, epochs=max_epoch, distributed=True)
